---
name: Workspace Focus on Session Start
description: Ensures that the focus is always set to the currently selected folder's root when a new session is initiated.
---

When a new session, task, or conversation is initiated:
- Always set your focus and working directory to the currently selected folder's `root` directory like to "VAPT-Secure" in case a files anywhere below it is currentl selected, within the workspace.
- Do not default to subdirectories or unrelated paths unless explicitly requested by the user.
